tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished 10th at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament in early March at Wolong Lake GC in Liuzhou to secure fully-exempt playing privileges for the entire season. His second-round 69 tied him for low-round-of-the-tournament honors during a week of cold, rainy conditions.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Made one appearance on the PGA TOUR China Series, playing, at the Hainan Open in Sanya, where he finished 66th.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T64th in 2015 at the Pingan Bank Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 47th in Par 3 Birdie or Better Leaders on the PGA Tour China Series.
